# Epics — logical groups of work

Created via `/decompose <PRD>`. Each epic groups related tasks and is constrained by ADRs.

Format:
  EPIC-NNN-<slug>.md
  - parent_prd: PRD-NNN
  - constrained_by: [ADR-NNN, ADR-NNN]
  - tasks: [T-NNN, T-NNN, ...]
  - depends_on: [EPIC-NNN, ...]

EPIC files mirror to Outline `Project: <name> / Epics` (auto-publish).
